##### PROGRAMS #####

# Kitty is hardcoded into launching terminal programs,
# but if you use a different terminal all you need to
# do is replace "st" with the terminal of your choice

### ARandR
super + shift + a
    arandr

### Brave Browser
super + b
    brave

super + shift + b
    brave --incognito

### Bpytop System Monitor
ctrl + shift + Escape 
    st bpytop

### Calculator (KCalc)
super + shift + c
    kcalc

### Cava Music Visualizer
super + alt + a
    st cava 

### Chatterino
super + shift + h
    chatterino

